faqs.answer:
Yes. Axes scale state is subplot-local, so `loglog` in one panel doesn't affect neighbors.

```matlab
subplot(1, 2, 1);
loglog(x, x.^(-2));
subplot(1, 2, 2);
plot(x, x.^(-2)); % linear axes here
```
